title: Jenelle Evans Has a New Man and They Are Getting Pretty Wild Already
text:
Step aside, Nathan Griffin. You're so last season!
Teen Mom 2 's Jenelle Evans has a new man and she's showing him off! Which, makes sense, seeing as he's mad hot. Ladies and gentlemen (I see you out there reading Cosmo! No shame!), please meet David Eason!
Look, aren't they a handsome couple!?
Dinner last night. ☺️
A photo posted by Jenelle Evans (@j_evans8209) on Sep 24, 2015 at 9:14am PDT
Advertisement - Continue Reading Below And just yesterday, Jenelle and David went muddin'!
Caption explains it all. ☺️ #SoHappy @uncledave01
A photo posted by Jenelle Evans (@j_evans8209) on Oct 1, 2015 at 2:37pm PDT
Umm... that's adorable and looks like fun, but what is muddin'?! Can someone explain it to me. Do we have it in California and if so, where and who's going with me?
